data.description: Make your home ownership dreams come true with this charming 4 bedroom bungalow in the heart of St Helens. Close to river front, shops, restaurants and all of the Old Town activities. Features 4 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, large eat-in kitchen, fenced yard and oversized detached single car garage.
